Delete .xsd file found in souluion explorer
Open Data Source Tab and add new connection
When prompted with, Where will the application get data from?, select Database
When prompted with, What type of database model do you want o use?, select Dataset
On the next from select new connection and make sure data source is in Microsoft SQL Database file
On the same form search for students.mdf file and attach
Make sure connection is successful by clicking Test Connection and clik Ok
A form will pop up.....just click no ( if you click yes the database will reset each time the program runs)
Select tables and click finish
Program should now run properly with the database
